						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1518 (1596 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers gift of lands in Māyaṇa-nallūr situated in Tiruśirāpura-uśāvaḍi for various services to the god and the goddess in the temple by Viśvanāthanāyaka-Liṅgayanāyaka-Kṛishṇappanāyakkar. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1518, Durmukhi, Makara ba. 7, Friday, Hastā correspond regularly to 1596 A.D., December 31, Friday ·59, ·32.</hi></p>						

